NAME: Stress Survey
DESCRIPTION: Burnout being represented by emotional and or physical exhaustion of employees due to long term, incessant, work-induced stress can put at risk the achievement of important goals and a correct work life balance at a basis of a good Performance and climate. This questionnaire aims detecting any signal that might be interesting to follow up before it's too late.

NAME: Mood
DESCRIPTION: Checking continuously the "climate" of your Teammates with this questionnaire, listen to how they feel and if there are recognizable recurrent claims or feeling is a small step preceding more actions to establish the correct work life balance and avoid risky disengagement phenomena.
HEADER_TITLE: How was your mood over the last week?

NAME: Remote Working - Tell us your experience
DESCRIPTION: Remote Working - Tell us your experience
HEADER_TITLE: Remote Working - Tell us your experience
HEADER_DESCRIPTION: Thank you for taking the time to complete this survey - we ask you these questions so that we can understand how was your experience working remotely from home, what the pain points and margin of improvements.

NAME: Exit interview  - Tell us your experience
DESCRIPTION: Thank you for taking the time to complete this survey. We would like you to spend few minutes telling us how was your experience working with use, what didn’t work and how we can improve.
HEADER_TITLE: Exit interview  - Tell us your experience
HEADER_DESCRIPTION: Thank you for taking the time to complete this survey. We would like you to spend few minutes telling us how was your experience working with use, what didn’t work and how we can improve.

NAME: Onboarding Questionnaire
DESCRIPTION: This questionnaire can be used in an onboarding survey to gather feedback from new starters.

NAME: Feedback from the Manager
DESCRIPTION: This questionnaire is for managers to give feedback to new starters at the end of the onboarding period.

NAME: Feedback from the Employee
DESCRIPTION: This questionnaire is for new starters to share feedback and expectations at the end of the onboarding period.

NAME: Standard Candidate Interview Questionnaire
DESCRIPTION: This questionnaire can be linked to a Selection Step in order to collect feedback from a Candidate interview.

NAME: Training Effectiveness standard assessment form
DESCRIPTION: Use this form to assess the effectiveness of Training made by your employees.

NAME: Professional Interview
DESCRIPTION: L’entretien professionnel est un acte clé du management dans l’entreprise.  Au plan collectif, il constitue un pilier de la gestion des ressources humaines de l’entreprise et le cadre d’exercice de sa responsabilité en matière de formation.

NAME: Course Session Feedback from Learner
HEADER_TITLE: Help us improving your learning experience!
HEADER_DESCRIPTION: Your feedback is important. Tell us what worked for you and what didn't. We'll do it better the next time, thanks to your help.
